tatus":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-housing-communities-local-government","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_roles":[{"content_id":"84778f3a-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe HM Land Registry Board Chair works closely with the Chief Executive and Chief Land Registrar in leading the development of the organisation. The role has responsibility for ensuring that proper governance practices are followed and performance is monitored effectively.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-05-22T11:28:23Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-executive Chair","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84778fed-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Chief Operations Officer is responsible for all registration services, completing the register, customer services and client account management.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-05-22T11:17:23Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Operations Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84779092-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Chief Land Registrar is responsible for keeping the land registers and has all the powers, responsibilities and duties conferred and imposed by law in relation to that.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe Chief Land Registrar is also HM Land Registry’s Chief Executive and Principal Accounting Officer. This role is responsible for the efficient and effective day-to-day management of the organisation, including overseeing its objectives and the implementation of an approved business strategy and business plan.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2020-04-01T13:33:21Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Executive and Chief Land Registrar","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84779728-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eA Non-executive Board Member is responsible for constructively challenging, and providing guidance and support to, the Executive Board.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-01-07T14:30:42Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-executive board member and non-executive board member with responsibility for the Union","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"847797c7-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eA Non-executive Board Member is responsible for constructively challenging, and providing guidance and support to, the Executive Board.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-05-22T11:59:22Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-executive Board Member","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84779870-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Director of Finance and Business Services is responsible for the financial management of HM Land Registry and compliance with the general requirements of Government Accounting.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThey oversee the preparation of our annual report and accounts and are responsible for ensuring the key performance indicator for efficiency is achieved. They provide advice to the Chief Executive and the Portfolio Board on the regularity and propriety of expenditure and also provide advice on commercial contracts.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2017-06-16T08:50:28Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Finance and Business Services","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84779913-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eA Non-executive Board Member is responsible for constructively challenging, and providing guidance and support to, the Executive Board.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-05-22T11:55:45Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-executive Board Member","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"847799b5-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eA Non-executive Board Member is responsible for constructively challenging, and providing guidance and support to, the Executive Board.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-05-08T09:08:44Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-executive Board Members","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84779a50-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Director of Legal Services is the principal legal adviser to the Chief Land Registrar and to HM Land Registry. They take administrative decisions on casework matters, including indemnity claims, and on HM Land Registry litigation.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe role is responsible for ensuring HM Land Registry has effective legal services and directs the provision of geographic information services within HM Land Registry.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2017-04-03T07:44:02Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Legal Services","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84779b96-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Chief Information Officer (CIO) and Director of Information Systems is accountable and responsible for the Information Systems directorate. This includes the direction of HM Land Registry’s Information Services policies, practices and resources including its personnel, external contracts, enterprise architecture and information assets.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2017-04-03T07:47:30Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Information Systems","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84779c3a-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe role is accountable for:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eensuring HM Land Registry’s Business Strategy remains relevant in a changing market and that all change initiatives align with and support the strategy.\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ethe provision of project and programme management capabilities and governance\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eHM Land Registry’s international strategy and activities\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2017-04-03T07:48:08Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Acting Director of Strategy","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84779cd9-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe HR Director is responsible for setting and delivering HM Land Registry’s people strategy. This includes strategic workforce planning, leadership and management development, employee relations, wellbeing, learning and development, and ensuring colleagues have the tools and support they need to perform effectively. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe role also supports the organisation’s strategic objectives by embedding inclusive behaviours and effective performance management across HM Land Registry.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-03-05T09:38:41Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Human Resources","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"22d9a1bc-e2a5-4469-b40f-6c94f13aef2b","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eA Non-executive Board Member is responsible for constructively challenging, and providing guidance and support to, the Executive Board.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-05-22T12:00:03Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-executive Board Member","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"1f409464-6ccf-4d26-baaa-de77f48d36f7","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe director is responsible for:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003estrategy, delivery and improvement of digital services\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eworking with technical teams at all levels, from design through to development\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003edriving the successful delivery of digital projects\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ebusiness change, information management and assurance\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ecollaborating with executive colleagues and other programme senior responsible owners (SROs)\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003esupporting colleagues in driving changes to the provision of IT services\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2020-09-21T10:22:28Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Interim Director of Digital, Data and Technology","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"791cd9f7-7f79-480a-ba7e-63ca4b99c4d2","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Director of Transformation is responsible for the successful design, implementation, integration, and delivery of transformation programmes resulting from our business strategy.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-05-22T11:15:34Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Transformation","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"ed66ccb2-efde-4b3d-bd62-c6c15ddce853","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eIn support of the Chief Land Registrar, the role has responsibility for the legal framework for land registration in England and Wales and its administrative application by HM Land Registry.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-07-04T14:56:21Z","schema_name":"role","title":"General Counsel and Deputy Chief Land Registrar","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"c3f9393d-df5f-40cd-8157-4946eb96f411","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eA Non-executive Board Member is responsible for constructively challenging, and providing guidance and support to, the Executive Board.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-05-22T11:56:50Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-executive Board Member","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"501d5c8e-275d-4eef-8617-214a107c6128","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eA Non-executive Board Member is responsible for constructively challenging, and providing guidance and support to, the Executive Board.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-05-22T11:55:02Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-executive Board Member","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"49bd8777-da53-48e9-9a64-c991331a046a","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Acting Director of Finance and Business Services is responsible for the financial management of HM Land Registry and compliance with the general requirements of Government Accounting, including the preparation of our Annual Report and Accounts.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThey are responsible for strategic planning and performance, including the medium term financial plan and monitoring performance against our key performance indicators.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThey are also responsible for our Internal Audit function, for providing professional procurement services to the organisation, undertaking major procurements and ensuring contracts are managed effectively, and for delivering professional and sustainable property services across our 14 offices, as well as business continuity, physical and personnel security, and health and safety policy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2018-06-18T10:16:07Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Acting Director of Finance and Business Services","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"9f2979da-29c3-447c-bc4e-91462d321a04","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Chief Land Registrar is responsible for keeping the land registers and has all the powers, responsibilities and duties conferred and imposed by law in relation to that.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe Chief Land Registrar is also HM Land Registry’s Chief Executive and Accounting Officer. This role is responsible for the efficient and effective day-to-day management of the organisation, including overseeing its objectives and the implementation of an approved business strategy and business plan.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-05-22T10:47:06Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Acting Chief Executive and Chief Land Registrar","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"83436d67-6be0-444a-a568-16c5a3835170","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Acting General Counsel and Deputy Chief Land Registrar is responsible for the legal framework for land registration in England and Wales and its administrative application by HM Land Registry. They are also responsible for the provision of legal services related to registration within HM Land Registry.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-08-05T12:10:08Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Acting General Counsel and Deputy Chief Land Registrar","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"c147bf33-7aed-443a-93ff-5dfcef99b9ab","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Chief Financial Officer is responsible for the financial management of HM Land Registry and compliance with the general requirements of Government Accounting.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThey oversee the preparation of our annual accounts and are responsible for ensuring the key performance indicator for efficiency is achieved. They provide advice to the Chief Executive and the Portfolio Board on the regularity and propriety of expenditure and also provide advice on commercial contracts.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-05-22T11:25:57Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Financial Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"fe6988f3-b5ca-446c-907b-9aa88ecab749","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Director of HR leads on all people and culture matters at HM Land Registry. They report directly to the Chief Executive and Chief Land Registrar and is a member of the Senior Executive Team. They also chair the People and Estates Committee, and attends the Remuneration and Nominations Committee.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe role involves the provision of pragmatic but creative and visionary people solutions, which have tangible business benefits, align to the Business Strategy and promote a modern and forward-thinking work culture.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-01-22T15:38:44Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Human Resources and Organisation Development","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"6bfb69f0-e406-4ad1-b642-bfd88cf024e8","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eA Non-executive Board Member is responsible for constructively challenging, and providing guidance and support to, the Executive Board.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-08-29T12:33:31Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-executive Board Member","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"df1c9be5-3747-4526-a8af-06142d43a3ed","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe role has responsibility for the legal framework for land registration in England and Wales and its administrative application by HM Land Registry and deputises for the Chief Executive and Chief Land Registrar.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-07-04T12:59:52Z","schema_name":"role","title":"General Counsel, Deputy Chief Executive and Deputy Chief Land Registrar","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"db29e322-fb18-4c12-b0a9-a4b23d11d451","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eA Non-executive Board Member is responsible for constructively challenging, and providing guidance and support to, the Executive Board.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-06-11T12:24:46Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-executive Board Member","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"5676fac2-2cd9-423d-8454-a85be98a363c","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eA Non-executive Board Member is responsible for constructively challenging, and providing guidance and support to, the Executive Board.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-01-12T10:50:32Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-executive Board Member","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"24c835a3-f71b-42ce-9035-c168218b7987","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe role has responsibility for corporate strategy, external engagement, customer relations, service design and product management, policy development and enterprise design and deputises for the Chief Executive.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-01-06T10:35:29Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of Customer and Strategy Group, Deputy Chief Executive, and Deputy Chief Land Registrar","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"cd3be7cf-7412-430e-9b80-27cbf33b5c87","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe director is responsible for:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eoverseeing the organisation’s transformational ambition and the programmes to deliver on this\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003edevelopment, operation and maintenance of new and existing technology solutions and systems\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eworking across the organisation and sector to deliver service improvements for both customers and staff\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eensuring the organisation’s technology is resilient and effectively underpins HMLR’s business operations\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ecollaborating with and supporting colleagues to successfully embed changes\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-11-08T10:15:17Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Transformation \u0026 Technology Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"bd373d5f-8233-4114-8587-af362481dbc5","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eA Non-executive Committee Member provides independent support and expertise for one or more sub-committee of HM Land Registry Board.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-08-21T14:21:04Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-executive Committee Member","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"e2feb15a-d3ae-40de-bc19-c7feb6751774","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe role is accountable for driving service excellence and operational performance in the delivery of our Land Registration services over the medium to long term for the benefit of our customers.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-11-06T11:47:34Z","sch