_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-09-10T13:38:30Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Interim Chief Financial Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"635bb5e6-9e36-4b88-9b52-afa215059ebc","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Interim Director of Human Resources and Organisational Development is responsible for the development and implementation of the ‘people strategy’ for the organisation.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-09-09T15:03:41Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Interim HR and Organisational Development Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"dc7c26a2-a26a-4c4f-a315-4133d8c8878c","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe Interim Director of Human Resources and Organisational Development is responsible for the development and implementation of the ‘people strategy’ for the organisation.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-09-10T13:42:57Z","schema_name":"role","title":" Interim Director of Human Resources and Organisation Development","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"33c3098e-fae0-49a8-bb55-75a0d8eb09f0","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThe interim role has responsibility for corporate strategy, external engagement, customer relations, service design and product management, policy development and enterprise design.\u003c/p\u003e\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-01-23T09:09:24Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Interim Director of Customer and Strategy","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D69","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/land-registry","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/land-registry","base_path":"/government/organisations/land-registry","content_id":"5c54ae5